Mediaset Says Italy Ad Sales Recovering Strongly in April

-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-04-20T13:42:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/mediaset-says-italy-ad-sales-recovering-strongly-in-april.html
Mediaset SpA (MS)  Chairman Fedele Confalonieri said there has been a “strong recovery” in
advertising sales this month.  Confalonieri, speaking at the company’s annual general
meeting today in Milan, said advertising revenue in Italy was
“flat” in the first quarter. Ad sales fell 1 percent to 2
percent in the quarter, the company said.  Mediaset, controlled by Italian Prime Minister  Silvio
Berlusconi , rose as much as 3 percent in Milan and traded at
4.37 euros, up 1.6 percent, at 3:21 p.m.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini at 
